OL,3,CWoman fears being kept alive to suffer
OL,4,Cinstead of being allowed to die
OL,6,FA woman with neurodegenerative
OL,7,Fconditions has said that an assisted
OL,8,Fdeath would allow her to "die with
OL,9,Fdignity, tranquility and calm".
OL,11,FAnne Jappie, from Cheltenham, wants to
OL,12,Flive. But she says her
OL,13,Fneurodegenerative conditions mean that
OL,14,F- down the line - she might prefer to
OL,15,Fdie.
