OL,3,CWoman fears being kept alive to suffer
OL,4,Cinstead of being allowed to die
OL,6,FShe told ITV News: "If I get to the
OL,7,Fpoint where I think I can't do this
OL,8,Fanymore... I can be allowed to die
OL,9,Fwith dignity and tranquility and calm
OL,10,F- maybe with a final blast - here at
OL,11,Fhome. It's just civilised."
OL,13,FAssisted dying is illegal in the UK.
OL,14,FBut a bill introduced to Parliament on
OL,15,FWednesday 16 October could give
OL,16,Fterminally ill people the right to end
OL,17,Ftheir lives.
OL,19,FOpponents argue that people would feel
OL,20,Fpressured to die.
