OL,3,CWoman fears being kept alive to suffer
OL,4,Cinstead of being allowed to die
OL,6,FThis is called assisted suicide. It is
OL,7,Flegal in Switzerland and some 350
OL,8,FBritons have travelled there to end
OL,9,Ftheir lives.
OL,11,FAnne says she can't, and does not want
OL,12,Fto, travel to Switzerland but wants to
OL,13,Fdie at home.
OL,15,F"It's my decision," Anne said. "It's
OL,16,Fmy circumstance. I don't particularly
OL,17,Fappreciate other people, perhaps with
OL,18,Fthe best will of the world, telling me
OL,19,Fwhat I can cope with, put up with and
OL,20,Fwhat I should tolerate.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
