OL,3,CWoman fears being kept alive to suffer
OL,4,Cinstead of being allowed to die
OL,6,FBut Anne described that time as "three
OL,7,Fyears of hell", adding: "She was
OL,8,Fcrying, she was in pain, she had
OL,9,Ffurther mini strokes and fits."
OL,11,FCritics of assisted dying say that its
OL,12,Flegalisation could put pressure on
OL,13,Fmany to end their lives.
OL,15,FBut Anne says that measures can be put
OL,16,Fin place to avoid people being
OL,17,Fpressured to die.
